         b'ssive.</font></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <t'
         b'd align="left"><b><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="-1">DC(B)02abc<'
         b'/font></b></td>\n            <td align="center"><b><font face="Ar'
         b'ial,Helvetica" size="-1">Biometric\nSecurity\nInterfaces</font></b'
         b'></td>\n            <td align="left"><font face="Arial,Helvetica"'
         b' size="-1">Passwords\nhave their\nproblems as access control keys.'
         b' The future is probably biometrics. In\nthe\nfilm "True Lies" Arni'
