         b' face="Arial,Helvetica" size="-1">DC(B)03</font></b></td>\n      '
         b'      <td align="center"><b><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="-1">F'
         b'low\nanalysis for Idealised Algol<br>\n            </font></b></td'
         b'>\n            <td align="left"><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size'
         b'="-1">Idealised\nAlgol is an expressive, imperative language with'
         b' procedures and side\neffects. It is essentially a lambda calculu'
         b's with state so it has\nlambda variables and state variables. Tog'
         b'ether with some collaborators\nI have developed a flow analysis f'
