         b'Horse security attacks.&nbsp; There exists an\nimplementation of '
         b'this flow analysis for the While language (the basic\nimperative '
         b'language without procedures) and this project will build on\nthat'
         b' to extend this to Idealised Algol. There could be a steep learn'
         b'ing\ncurve in the early part of the project but once that is past'
         b' the\nstudent will have a clearly defined goal and a considerable'
         b' base on\nwhich to build. Wanted: someone unfrightened by compile'
         b'r technology and\nexpressive languages.<br>\n            </font></'
