         b'ge (often called the While language). This\nuses Information Theo'
         b'ry to measure the amount of secret information\nthat can be leake'
         b'd via a Trojan Horse attack on a program. The student\nwill need '
         b'to write a parser and build the underlying graph which is\nused b'
         b'y the analysis.<br>\n            </font></td>\n          </tr>\n   '
