         b'="center"><b><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="-1">Implementing'
         b'\nPart Whole Statecharts</font></b></td>\n            <td align="l'
         b'eft"><font face="Arial,Helvetica" size="-1">Statecharts\nare\na gr'
